- RefreshToken event for monitoring integrations
- onTokenExpired callback for custom expiry handling
- LogoutRedirectUri for RP-Initiated Logout
- Token validation utility function

### 🐛 **Critical Bug Fixes:**
- **Security:** CSRF protection on authorization callback + token redaction in logs
- **SSO:** Session invalidation edge case on token expiry (with migration guide link)
